{"tid":155989,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港故：單親童每日哭句鐘　寄養姨姨以愛拭淚","createTime":"2017-03-14T12:22:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-14T12:41:50.000Z","uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4e5dddae6b4d446acfe3e109bba245e7a33f8071","tid":155989,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T12:22:54.000Z","msg":"「我的家，有爸爸，有媽媽&hellip;&hellip;」友誠一字一句地朗讀出課本上的文章。然而，他日常的生活中，沒有爸爸，也沒有媽媽。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">友誠的爸爸在他小時候去世，媽媽又長居內地，沒辦法來港照顧他。自小在寄養家庭中長大，友誠只能在假期回內地，與媽媽共聚天倫。</span><br />\n<br />\n照顧他的姨姨丘太，家中住着三個寄養的男生，她憶述友誠剛搬來時的情況：「他當時很瘦，經常都會大哭，一哭就是一個小時，但在我們家中住久了，慢慢愈哭愈少。」<br />\n<br />\n今天的友誠，是一個白白胖胖、笑容滿面的男生。但他心裡仍然希望，有一天，可以和媽媽住在一起&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n鳴謝：香港家庭福利會<br />\n=======================<br />\n《港&middot;故》：東網電視每周專題習作，講故事、講香港人的故事。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170312/bkn-20170312120045036-0312_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170312%2Fbkn-20170312120045036-0312_00822_001.html&d=3A5iQKMTOMHlOvaIjHeReu9M5Ue6CDmcYDZznX2R1Ws%3D&h=92fd65b1\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170312/bkn-20170312120045036-0312_00822_001.html</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c8020abd5c608d0723e193dffa6cdf84f1d4deb","tid":155989,"uid":55924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T12:24:39.000Z","msg":"弱智？咁辛苦唔番大陸住？"},{"pid":"e8c4de900ab68033d54872b09460221928f7085f","tid":155989,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T12:28:37.000Z","msg":"東網電視每周專題習作，講故事、<span style=\"color: red;\">講香港人</span>的故事。<br />\n<br />\n香港人在哪??<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2223d5b41dbff4cdfeba8af433015cfa6f3dcca2","tid":155989,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T12:35:25.000Z","msg":"一係去支那團聚一係落去團聚"},{"pid":"348d9acbdbf1a7b364c2d78f42